@TomSweeneyRedHat of course!! Actually that you mention it, It took me a while to set up my machine to build buildah... 

The [CONTRIBUTING](https://github.com/containers/buildah/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) doc has room for improvements IMHO. Sth similar to what [openshift/origin has](https://github.com/openshift/origin/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.adoc#openshift-development) would be great. I mean, a more detailed step by step guide, with dependencies, packages needed, etc. 

Just my 2 cents ;).
